\begin_inset Formula $g\circ f$
\end_inset

 están bien definidas, y dadas por
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
f\circ g & =\left\{ \left(2,-3\right)\right\} \\
g\circ f & =\left\{ \left(1,a\right),\left(a,-3\right),\left(-1,-3\right),\left(2,-1\right)\right\} .
\end{align*}

